sentences.english: Your chart is looking really good this week & causing the attention of others to be riveted directly upon you…

sentences.english: According to my father, the chart of my sky curiously resembles a pentagram .
sentences.chinese: 根據父親所說，我的星空命盤奇如五星之狀。

sentences.english: The part of your chart being lit up by the New Moon is ruled by Jupiter-the planet of expansion.
sentences.chinese: 你命盤裏被新月照亮的區域由擴張性質的木星掌管。

sentences.english: This week's chart energy causes you to really stand out & shine in the eyes of others...
